data.text: @VanderpumpRules Why are we still talking about this douche? #lisaisofflimits

@VanderpumpRules I thought my ex was the biggest A-hole in history!! My jaw dropped several times after hearing the shit that spewed out of his mouth last night. What a classless POS the way he spoke to Lisa, and not saying a word to Stassi when she was begging him. Not sure why she was though.

@VanderpumpRules Not sure if I've ever seen a bigger chump than Little Patrick. Bad look on national cable TV. Lisa was right to belittle him for all to see. Can't believe Stassi was begging him not to break up with her. If that was Jax, she'd given him an earful of cuss words.
@VanderpumpRules I'm not a fan of either of them, however last night was the first time I actually felt a tinge of sympathy for S.S. Glad to hear she's moved on.
@VanderpumpRules Yuck  why is he still getting press notes? POS with a man bun
@VanderpumpRules Don’t give him any notoriety... he is a puke and doesn’t bring anything to show... PLEASE PLEASE!!  Make him go away..🙏🙏
